text: Ashkadar () is a rural locality (a village) in Otradovsky Selsoviet, Sterlitamaksky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 71 as of 2010. There are 4 streets. == Geography == It is located 11 km from Sterlitamak, 7 km from Novaya Otradovka. == References == Category:Rural localities in Sterlitamaksky District
title: Ashkadar
